{"version":2,"title":"Red Mars","author":"Kim Stanley Robinson","state":{"lastAnalyzedIndex":5,"result":{"characters":[{"name":"John Boone","aliases":["Boone"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Red Letter Days","currentLocation":"Space station","description":"An officer aboard the spacecraft, part of the mission to Mars.","relationships":[{"character":"Maya Toitovna","relationship":"Works with"},{"character":"Frank Case","relationship":"Works with"},{"character":"Hiroko Ai","relationship":"Engages in games with (Frank)"}],"recentEvents":"Discussed the nature of leadership with Frank while looking at Mars; played jump games with Frank and Hiroko."},{"name":"Frank Pottinger","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Crucible","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"One of the first humans to set foot on Mars","relationships":[{"character":"John Boone","relationship":"Colleague"},{"character":"Anna Kushak","relationship":"Colleague"},{"character":"Hiroko Ikuda","relationship":"Colleague"}],"recentEvents":"Discussed in the prologue as one of the founding characters of the Mars settlement"},{"name":"Anna Kushak","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Crucible","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"One of the first humans to set foot on Mars","relationships":[{"character":"John Boone","relationship":"Colleague"},{"character":"Frank Pottinger","relationship":"Colleague"},{"character":"Hiroko Ikuda","relationship":"Colleague"}],"recentEvents":"Discussed in the prologue as one of the founding characters of the Mars settlement"},{"name":"Hiroko Ikuda","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Crucible","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"One of the first humans to set foot on Mars","relationships":[{"character":"John Boone","relationship":"Colleague"},{"character":"Frank Pottinger","relationship":"Colleague"},{"character":"Anna Kushak","relationship":"Colleague"}],"recentEvents":"Discussed in the prologue as one of the founding characters of the Mars settlement"},{"name":"Frank Chalmers","aliases":["Mayor"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter title where they last appeared","currentLocation":"Torus D (on the spaceship)","description":"A leader of the mission, possibly a native of Mars, often displaying a sense of isolation and reserve.","relationships":[{"character":"Maya Khusite","relationship":"Had a brief, complicated affair which has now ended"}],"recentEvents":"Had a complex romantic encounter with Maya Khusite, which ended without any resolution or meaningful conversation."},{"name":"Maya Toitovna","aliases":["Maya"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Red Letter Days","currentLocation":"Space station","description":"A Russian psychologist on a spacecraft to Mars.","relationships":[{"character":"Frank Case","relationship":"Had a brief affair with"},{"character":"John Boone","relationship":"Works with"},{"character":"Hiroko Ai","relationship":"Engages in games with (Frank)"}],"recentEvents":"Encountered a mysterious stranger in the farm and pursued him through several cylinders without finding him."},{"name":"Sax Russell","aliases":["Sax"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter 22: Meditations and Revelations","currentLocation":"New City","description":"A geologist and terraforming expert, Sax is a key engineer in the transformation of Mars into a more habitable environment, often at odds with political figures.","relationships":[{"character":"Frank Chalmers","relationship":"Former adversary turned ally"},{"character":"Maya Toitovna","relationship":"Colleague and friend"},{"character":"John Boone","relationship":"Former rival"}],"recentEvents":"Sax helps chase after a group of strangers who attacked John Boone, later guiding Frank and Maya to the location where John was found."},{"name":"Michel Duval","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Prologue","currentLocation":"Antarctica (McMurdo Station and Wright Valley)","description":"A psychiatrist sent to observe the first group of colonists bound for Mars.","relationships":[{"character":"Charles York","relationship":"Chairman of the selection committee"}],"recentEvents":"Sent to observe the finalists at McMurdo Station and later moved to Wright Valley where he lived with them in habitats and monitored their interactions."},{"name":"Charles York","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Prologue","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Chairman of the selection committee for the Mars colonists.","relationships":[{"character":"Michel Duval","relationship":"Asked Duval to observe the finalists"}],"recentEvents":"Selected Michel Duval to observe the finalists in Antarctica."},{"name":"Maya Khusite","aliases":["Maya"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter title where they last appeared","currentLocation":"Torus D (on the spaceship)","description":"The deputy commander of the mission and a key figure in the group, often displaying a practical and strategic mindset.","relationships":[{"character":"Frank Chalmers","relationship":"Had a brief, complicated affair which has now ended"}],"recentEvents":"Had a complex romantic encounter with Frank Chalmers, which ended without any resolution or meaningful conversation."},{"name":"Frank Case","aliases":["Captain Frank"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Red Letter Days","currentLocation":"Space station","description":"The captain of the spacecraft, overseeing the mission to Mars.","relationships":[{"character":"Maya Toitovna","relationship":"Was romantically involved with"},{"character":"John Boone","relationship":"Works with"}],"recentEvents":"Discussed leadership and survival issues with Maya; encountered Maya and John while looking at Mars."},{"name":"Hiroko Ai","aliases":["Hiroko"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Red Letter Days","currentLocation":"Space station","description":"A Japanese engineer aboard the spacecraft, engaged in physical challenges like jumps.","relationships":[{"character":"Maya Toitovna","relationship":"Engages in games with (Frank)"},{"character":"Frank Case","relationship":"Engages in games with"}],"recentEvents":"Challenged Frank to a jumping game and showed exceptional skills."}],"locations":[{"name":"Mars","description":"The fourth planet from the sun, which has been terraforming since its colonization by humans"},{"name":"New City","description":"A tent city built in the valley of a Martian river, serving as the primary settlement for Martian colonists. It is the stage for a great celebration where the city's sealing is marked, but also where tensions flare and tragedy ensues."},{"name":"McMurdo Station","description":"Base in Antarctica where the initial meeting of the finalists occurs."},{"name":"Wright Valley","description":"The largest of Antarctica’s Dry Valleys where the colonists lived in habitats for over a year."},{"name":"Torus D","description":"One of the sections of the spaceship where the main characters spend time dining, conversing, and walking."},{"name":"Farm","description":"An area on the spacecraft used for growing crops, where Maya was harvesting cabbages."}],"summary":"Maya encounters a mysterious stranger in a greenhouse-like part of the spacecraft and pursues him through the ship. Her colleagues Frank and John discuss leadership and the motivations for the mission, which has caused friction among their crew members."},"snapshots":[{"index":0,"result":{"characters":[{"name":"John Boone","aliases":["no known aliases"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Crucible","currentLocation":"Mars","description":"A key figure in the early colonization of Mars, known for his leadership and physical strength. Has a calm demeanor and is skilled in conflict resolution.","relationships":[{"character":"Frank Pottinger","relationship":"conflict"}],"recentEvents":"Has been involved in the decision-making processes and interpersonal conflicts among the early settlers."},{"name":"Frank Pottinger","aliases":["no known aliases"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Crucible","currentLocation":"Mars","description":"A biochemist and one of the early settlers of Mars, involved in scientific research but also confrontational and at times confronts John Boone.","relationships":[{"character":"John Boone","relationship":"conflict"}],"recentEvents":"Has been involved in the establishment and challenges of the initial Mars settlement."},{"name":"Anna Kushak","aliases":["no known aliases"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Crucible","currentLocation":"Mars","description":"A scientist and one of the early Mars settlers, has a role in understanding and dealing with the Martian environment's challenges.","relationships":[{"character":"John Boone","relationship":"conflict/interaction"}],"recentEvents":"Has been a participant in discussions and conflicts regarding the use and ethics of Martian resources."},{"name":"Hiroko Ikuda","aliases":["no known aliases"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Crucible","currentLocation":"Mars","description":"An engineer and artist, one of the primary figures among the initial Mars colonists, known for her creativity and leadership.","relationships":[{"character":"John Boone","relationship":"conflict/interaction"}],"recentEvents":"Has been involved in debates and decisions related to the survival and future of the Mars settlement."}],"locations":[{"name":"Mars","description":"The red planet, where the first human settlers are struggling to establish a new habitat, braving harsh conditions and internal conflicts."}],"summary":"The narrative is set on Mars, where early settlers are embroiled in the process of establishing a settlement. Tensions arise among key figures such as John Boone, Frank Pottinger, Anna Kushak, and Hiroko Ikuda, focusing on both the environmental challenges and interpersonal dynamics."}},{"index":1,"result":{"characters":[{"name":"John Boone","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Crucible","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"One of the first humans to set foot on Mars","relationships":[{"character":"Frank Pottinger","relationship":"Colleague"},{"character":"Anna Kushak","relationship":"Colleague"},{"character":"Hiroko Ikuda","relationship":"Colleague"}],"recentEvents":"Discussed in the prologue as one of the founding characters of the Mars settlement"},{"name":"Frank Pottinger","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Crucible","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"One of the first humans to set foot on Mars","relationships":[{"character":"John Boone","relationship":"Colleague"},{"character":"Anna Kushak","relationship":"Colleague"},{"character":"Hiroko Ikuda","relationship":"Colleague"}],"recentEvents":"Discussed in the prologue as one of the founding characters of the Mars settlement"},{"name":"Anna Kushak","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Crucible","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"One of the first humans to set foot on Mars","relationships":[{"character":"John Boone","relationship":"Colleague"},{"character":"Frank Pottinger","relationship":"Colleague"},{"character":"Hiroko Ikuda","relationship":"Colleague"}],"recentEvents":"Discussed in the prologue as one of the founding characters of the Mars settlement"},{"name":"Hiroko Ikuda","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Crucible","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"One of the first humans to set foot on Mars","relationships":[{"character":"John Boone","relationship":"Colleague"},{"character":"Frank Pottinger","relationship":"Colleague"},{"character":"Anna Kushak","relationship":"Colleague"}],"recentEvents":"Discussed in the prologue as one of the founding characters of the Mars settlement"}],"