ovna","relationship":"Colleague and friend"},{"character":"John Boone","relationship":"Former rival"}],"recentEvents":"Sax helps chase after a group of strangers who attacked John Boone, later guiding Frank and Maya to the location where John was found."},{"name":"Michel Duval","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Prologue","currentLocation":"Antarctica (McMurdo Station and Wright Valley)","description":"A psychiatrist sent to observe the first group of colonists bound for Mars.","relationships":[{"character":"Charles York","relationship":"Chairman of the selection committee"}],"recentEvents":"Sent to observe the finalists at McMurdo Station and later moved to Wright Valley where he lived with them in habitats and monitored their interactions."},{"name":"Charles York","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Prologue","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Chairman of the selection committee for the Mars colonists.","relationships":[{"character":"Michel Duval","relationship":"Asked Duval to observe the finalists"}],"recentEvents":"Selected Michel Duval to observe the finalists in Antarctica."},{"name":"Maya Khusite","aliases":["Maya"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"Chapter title where they last appeared","currentLocation":"Torus D (on the spaceship)","description":"The deputy commander of the mission and a key figure in the group, often displaying a practical and strategic mindset.","relationships":[{"character":"Frank Chalmers","relationship":"Had a brief, complicated affair which has now ended"}],"recentEvents":"Had a complex romantic encounter with Frank Chalmers, which ended without any resolution or meaningful conversation."},{"name":"Frank Case","aliases":["Captain Frank"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Red Letter Days","currentLocation":"Space station","description":"The captain of the spacecraft, overseeing the mission to Mars.","relationships":[{"character":"Maya 